bleme und zur politischen und militärischen Entscheidungsfindung im Rahmen der internationalen Krisenprävention und -bekämpfung beitragen können.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 4aBalkan. 4aMilitärgeschichte. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh1 aAdanir, Fikret, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBreitwieser, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChiari, Bernhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aChiari, Bernhard, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aClewing, Konrad, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEhlert, Hans, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGahlen, Gundula, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGroß, Gerhard P., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGroß, Gerhard P., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHacisalihoğlu, Mehmet, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHöbelt, Lothar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJakir, Aleksandar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKeßelring, Agilolf, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKronenbitter, Günther, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aOrtner, Μ. Christian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPahl, Magnus.1 aPotempa, Harald, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aReemtsma, Jan Philipp, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchiel, Rüdiger, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchlaffer, Rudolf J., econtri